title: Maren Morris and Alicia Keys Will Sweep You Off Your Feet With This Performance
text:
Maren Morris and Alicia Keys 2017 Grammys Performance Video Maren Morris and Alicia Keys Will Sweep You Off Your Feet With This Performance February 12, 2017 by Monica Sisavat 2 Shares 
Maren Morris and Alicia Keys were among the many performers at the Grammys on Sunday night, and the singers teamed up for a beautiful duet of Maren's hit song "Once." Country fan or not, this performance is just plain beautiful and will sweep you right off your feet.
